<div class="container mt-4">
  <h1>Welcome to Padraig McCauley's POS System</h1>
  <p>Student ID: 20123744</p>
  <p>This Point of Sale system is designed to allow users to manage sales efficiently from one central point. It provides comprehensive tools for handling items, orders, and analytics. Below is a brief overview of the features available on each page:</p>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h2>Item Management</h2>
      <p>In the <strong>Item</strong> section, you can:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Add new items</li>
        <li>View all items</li>
        <li>Update existing items</li>
        <li>Delete items</li>
      </ul>
      <%= link_to 'Manage Items', items_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h2>Order Management</h2>
      <p>In the <strong>Order</strong> section, you can:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Create new orders</li>
        <li>View order details</li>
        <li>Edit and update orders</li>
        <li>Remove orders from the system</li>
      </ul>
      <%= link_to 'Manage Orders', orders_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h2>Analytics</h2>
      <p>In the <strong>Analytics</strong> section, you can:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Filter and view order data</li>
        <li>Analyze item sales</li>
        <li>Review order trends over time</li>
        <li>Gain insights from data analysis</li>
      </ul>
      <%= link_to 'View Analytics', analytics_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
